overview.en: YLchina (DYLC) is high-quality block-chain assets authorized and launched by the First Travelling Net (Denmark Coex Company). The First Travelling Net is devoted to providing low-cost, highly-transparent and highly-efficient business trip management services to global middle and small-sized enterprises, departments governed by district-level and county-level governments as well as public institutions through construction of professionalization, branding and networking. Besides, it strives to establish a cloud platform based on the development of block-chain technology and containing multiple chain combinations, including tem building, incentive travel, meeting training, guide service, special local products, etc. for business trip clients from enterprises and all the merchants.
overview.zh: YLchina（DYLC易履程）是由第一差旅网授权（  丹麦Coex 公司 ）推出的优质区块链资产。第一差旅网致力于并通过专业化、品牌化、网络化的建设，专注于全球范围内中小企业、区县政府所辖部门及企事业单位提供低成本、高透明、高效率的公务差旅管理服务，同时为企业差旅客户和所有商家搭建一个基于区块链技术开发的包括团队拓展、奖励旅游、会议培训、向导服务、当地特产在内的多个链条组合的云平台
